---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 14, 2026';

// Schema.org WebPage
const webPageSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Terms of Service",
  "description": "Terms of Service for Suparank - AI-powered SEO content creation platform using MCP.",
  "url": "https://suparank.io/terms",
  "dateModified": "2026-01-14",
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Suparank",
    "url": "https://suparank.io"
  }
};
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Suparank"
  description="Terms of Service for Suparank - AI-powered SEO content creation platform using MCP."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(webPageSchema)} />
  </Fragment>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="section-label mb-3 block">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <div class="prose prose-invert">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using Suparank ("Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
            If you do not agree to these terms, do not use the Service.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Suparank is an AI-powered SEO content creation platform that connects to your AI client
            (Claude Desktop, Cursor, ChatGPT, or similar) via the Model Context Protocol (MCP).
            The Service provides tools for keyword research, content writing, optimization, and publishing.
          </p>

          <h2>3. Account Registration</h2>
          <p>
            To use certain features of the Service, you must create an account at app.suparank.io.
            You are responsible for:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Providing accurate and complete registration information</li>
            <li>Maintaining the security of your account credentials and API keys</li>
            <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
            <li>Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized use</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. API Keys and Security</h2>
          <p>
            Your API keys are sensitive credentials. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Keep your API keys confidential and secure</li>
            <li>Not share API keys with unauthorized parties</li>
            <li>Revoke and regenerate keys if you suspect compromise</li>
            <li>Accept responsibility for all usage under your API keys</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to use the Service to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Generate spam, misleading, or deceptive content</li>
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights of others</li>
            <li>Distribute malware or engage in hacking activities</li>
            <li>Overwhelm our systems with excessive requests</li>
            <li>Resell or redistribute the Service without authorization</li>
            <li>Generate content that promotes hate, violence, or illegal activities</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>6. Content Ownership</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Your Content:</strong> You retain ownership of all content you create using the Service.
            You grant us a limited license to process your content solely for providing the Service.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>AI-Generated Content:</strong> Content generated by AI through our Service is provided
            as-is. You are responsible for reviewing, editing, and ensuring the accuracy of all generated
            content before publication.
          </p>

          <h2>7. Third-Party Integrations</h2>
          <p>
            The Service integrates with third-party platforms including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>WordPress and Ghost for publishing</li>
            <li>AI providers (Anthropic, OpenAI) for content generation</li>
            <li>Image generation services (fal.ai)</li>
            <li>SEO data providers for keyword research</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Your use of these integrations is subject to their respective terms of service.
            We are not responsible for third-party services.
          </p>

          <h2>8. Local Data Storage</h2>
          <p>
            The MCP client stores certain data locally on your machine (in ~/.suparank/), including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Configuration files</li>
            <li>Third-party credentials (WordPress passwords, CMS API keys)</li>
            <li>Session data and saved content</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            This local data never leaves your machine unless you explicitly publish or sync it.
            You are responsible for securing your local environment.
          </p>

          <h2>9. Service Availability</h2>
          <p>
            We strive to maintain high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted access.
            The Service may be temporarily unavailable for maintenance, updates, or circumstances
            beyond our control.
          </p>

          <h2>10. Pricing and Payment</h2>
          <p>
            During the early access period, the Service is free to use. Future pricing will be
            announced before any charges apply. We will provide reasonable notice before
            implementing paid features.
          </p>

          <h2>11. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
            WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE ERROR-FREE, SECURE, OR UNINTERRUPTED.
          </p>
          <p>
            AI-generated content may contain errors, inaccuracies, or outdated information.
            You are solely responsible for verifying and editing all content before use.
          </p>

          <h2>12. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, SUPARANK SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY
            INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING
            LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, OR BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES.
          </p>

          <h2>13. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service at any time for violation
            of these terms or for any other reason at our discretion. Upon termination, your
            right to use the Service ceases immediately.
          </p>

          <h2>14. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes
            constitutes acceptance of the modified terms. We will notify users of significant
            changes via email or through the Service.
          </p>

          <h2>15. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: legal@suparank.io</li>
            <li>Website: <a href="/contact">suparank.io/contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-foreground/90 leading-relaxed;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-10 mb-4;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-1;
  }
  .prose li {
    @apply text-foreground/90;
  }
  .prose a {
    @apply text-primary hover:text-primary-light underline;
  }
  .prose strong {
    @apply text-foreground font-semibold;
  }
</style>
